1. Compile Pyrosome
  
  On the server node, run setup_server.sh
  On the client node, run setup_client.sh

2. Run Pyrosome

  On the server node, run:
  ./shredder -c 16 -m30G

3. Run basic benchmark

  On the client node, run:
  wrk -t1 -c1 -d1s --latency -H "MS: 2" -H "L: 4" http://192.168.2.7:11211/microbenchmark/chain -R 10

  This command runs a service chain of 4 services each runs for 2 ms.
  The "MS" and "L" parameters can be modified.

